  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To learn more about the effect of 3, 4-Diaminopyridine (3,4-DAP) on patient diagnosed with
      Lambert-Eaton myasthenic syndrome (LEMS).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
